1
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:42,920
Good news.

2
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,680
Jueming, Coroner Li.

3
00:01:44,759 --> 00:01:45,960
Good news.

4
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:46,440
What is it?

5
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:47,840
Su Lang is saved.

6
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:50,880
The Liuli Orb has been recovered.

7
00:01:51,039 --> 00:01:53,880
And Lord Lu's wrongful conviction has been cleared.

8
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:55,039
Now Lord Lu

9
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:58,640
and Deputy Magistrate Li are both pleading for Su Lang.

10
00:01:58,960 --> 00:02:01,280
Su Lang is now spared from the death penalty.

11
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:03,760
Although his sentence hasn't been finalized yet,

12
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:06,400
his life is finally saved.

13
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:08,840
This is perhaps the best possible outcome.

14
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:11,080
Mr. Su, you can rest assured now.

15
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,680
I came today

16
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:15,680
to thank you all on behalf of my uncle.

17
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,370
If it weren't for all of you,

18
00:02:18,640 --> 00:02:20,240
things would hardly have turned around for my uncle.

19
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,160
Thank you all.

20
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:22,060
It was our duty.

21
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:24,400
We helped each other this time.

22
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:28,079
His Majesty already knows the Liuli Orb case is complicated.

23
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,680
Dali Temple has been ordered to intervene

24
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,480
to find out the truth

25
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:34,340
and get to the bottom of this as soon as possible.

26
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:37,000
Coroner Li, do you have the autopsy results?

27
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:44,680
Based on the length of the leg bones and spine,

28
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:48,400
we can deduce this person was about 6 feet tall.

29
00:02:48,480 --> 00:02:50,280
Moreover, the bones are thick

30
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,520
and the chest is broad,

31
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,980
indicating a burly build.

32
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:55,340
According to the records,

33
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:58,360
Constable Qin suffered a dislocation.

34
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:02,920
Plus, there was a sachet beside him.

35
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,480
Thus, we can deduce

36
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:07,760
that these are the remains of Qin Rui.

37
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:10,840
Can you find out where his fatal wound is?

38
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:15,200
There are traces of a heavy blow to the back of the head.

39
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:16,880
It is still obvious after so many years,

40
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:18,600
so it should be the fatal wound.

41
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:19,440
Also,

42
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:22,520
the ribs on the chest are broken.

43
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:25,240
They should have been broken by someone after his death.

44
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,920
Broken after death?

45
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:30,440
I was really foolish.

46
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:32,720
Why didn't I find this out back then?

47
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:38,160
That means out of the five charred bodies in the fire at the Qin family,

48
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:40,840
one of them was not Constable Qin,

49
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:42,320
but someone else.

50
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:43,920
In this way,

51
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:46,240
this fire was not a natural one.

52
00:03:46,440 --> 00:03:49,800
It might have been deliberately set by someone.

53
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:52,050
There is another body here.

54
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:56,400
Looking at these remains,

55
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:58,680
the fingertips are quite unusual.

56
00:03:58,840 --> 00:04:01,500
Normal people have fingers of distinct lengths

57
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:03,040
and different shapes.

58
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:08,080
But for this skeleton, the index and middle fingers are of equal length.

59
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:10,200
Its fingertip bones have been worn flat.

60
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:11,520
This is not normal.

61
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:17,320
I heard that great thieves in the martial arts world, in order to make their stealing techniques faster,

62
00:04:17,320 --> 00:04:19,920
would practice a special technique.

63
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:20,880
Over time,

64
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:23,680
their index and middle fingers, because of this technique,

65
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:26,560
will become of equal length and worn flat.

66
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,320
Therefore, it can be inferred that

67
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:32,440
this skeleton is highly likely that of a great thief.

68
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:33,840
So after all that,

69
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:35,720
it's just to make picking pockets easier.

70
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,159
These thieves.

71
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,760
But that makes sense.

72
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:43,040
This body should be Mo Ya's boss in the underworld,

73
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,320
Ye Xiao.

74
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:57,680
He's here.

75
00:04:58,680 --> 00:04:59,440
Mr. Lu.

76
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:03,840
Based on the current situation,

77
00:05:03,840 --> 00:05:05,320
the Glazed Orb was stolen.

78
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:06,680
After Ye Xiao was killed,

79
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:08,640
the killer didn't take the orb.

80
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:10,810
It is clear that the person behind this

81
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:13,440
was not after the Glazed Orb,

82
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,160
but your uncle.

83
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:16,080
Right.

84
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:19,080
If Mr. Lu falls,

85
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:21,360
who benefits the most?

86
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:25,600
My uncle has been a man of high moral character all his life,

87
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:26,840
kind to others,

88
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:28,280
and highly respected.

89
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:30,720
If we talk about making the deepest enemies

90
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,320
and sudden disturbances,

91
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:34,760
it must be the collapse of the Anlan Dam.

92
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:39,250
When the disaster struck, wails were heard everywhere.

93
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:42,840
My uncle was burdened with the heavy responsibility of dispatching disaster relief funds.

94
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:45,520
He went to the scene in person and spoke out in public.

95
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:47,880
This dam was only built a year ago,

96
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,480
and it collapsed.

97
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,400
It was definitely not a natural disaster.

98
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:54,060
There must be human negligence and corruption.

99
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:56,170
As soon as this was said,

100
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:57,960
it caused a great sensation.

101
00:05:58,640 --> 00:06:01,600
Since then, it has left many roots of trouble.

102
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,480
Yes.

103
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:05,360
When that disaster happened,

104
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:08,320
you were still young,

105
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:10,440
but I remember it vividly.

106
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:12,880
Many people died at that time.

107
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:17,760
This construction work was under the jurisdiction of the Ministry of Works.

108
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:23,160
My uncle suspected that Yuan Feng, the Minister of Works, lined his own pockets

109
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:28,000
and sought personal gain by cutting corners.

110
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:30,280
Yuan Feng.

111
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:34,040
My uncle once said he would thoroughly investigate this man.

112
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:39,040
You can't say that carelessly.

113
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:44,290
The Minister of Works is in charge of major national projects' design and construction.

114
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:46,320
If someone were to tamper with it,

115
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:48,050
it's not entirely impossible.

116
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,040
Thinking about it now,

117
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:52,520
the theft of the glazed orb

118
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:55,020
seems like a carefully planned conspiracy.

119
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:58,159
My uncle was inexplicably drawn into it,

120
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,860
and became deeply entangled.

121
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,200
With his imprisonment,

122
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:05,200
the Anlanti case seemed to be frozen instantly.

123
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,680
All parties fell silent by tacit agreement,

124
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:11,120
and the path to a thorough investigation was immediately blocked.

125
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,080
Yuan Feng

126
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:14,120
is a third-rank official in the court.

127
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:16,580
His power there is not to be underestimated.

128
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:19,440
If he really committed this crime,

129
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:21,080
investigating this case

130
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:22,920
will be extremely difficult.

131
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:25,040
I still have one question.

132
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:27,240
I remember Mo Ya once said

133
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:30,530
that Ye Xiao took the Liuli Orb to meet the client.

134
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:32,480
Then,

135
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:36,960
Constable Qin's remains are buried with Ye Xiao's.

136
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:40,040
Could it be that Constable Qin is Yuan Feng's minion?

137
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:43,600
Constable Qin was upright all his life.

138
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:46,520
He would never steal what was entrusted to him.

139
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:49,240
Elder Su, I was just guessing.

140
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:50,920
Back then, Constable Qin might have

141
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:53,720
just found clues about the stolen Glazed Pearl,

142
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:55,080
which led to him being silenced

143
00:07:55,080 --> 00:07:56,960
and his whole family being murdered.

144
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:59,640
Mr. Su, you and Constable Qin solved countless cases.

145
00:07:59,640 --> 00:08:02,840
I want to re-examine all the files of the cases you solved.

146
00:08:13,840 --> 00:08:15,840
Lord Minister, I've found out.

147
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:17,800
Jueming is just an ordinary Buliangren.

148
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:20,600
He has helped the yamen solve several major cases.

149
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,800
He is quite capable.

150
00:08:26,200 --> 00:08:28,400
No matter how beautiful a flower is,

151
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:31,600
if it grows where it shouldn'...

152
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:34,520
We must uproot it.

153
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:37,320
I know what to do.

154
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:18,010
Children kidnapped and missing at Niutou Mountain.

155
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:35,160
If you want the truth, go to the Qin residence in the north of the city.

156
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:04,360
Mr. Lu.

157
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:06,120
Mr. Lu.

158
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:11,880
Magistrate Zhao!

159
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:13,000
Magistrate Zhao, wait!

160
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,000
Magistrate Zhao!

161
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,680
Wait, wait!

162
00:11:15,800 --> 00:11:16,840
Please.

163
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,320
I have read the files.

164
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,320
Miss Li,

165
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:23,400
why are you in such a panic?

166
00:11:23,640 --> 00:11:24,680
Magistrate Zhao.

167
00:11:25,280 --> 00:11:28,280
Jueming is definitely not the murderer of Squire Lu.

168
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:29,960
There must be a hidden truth behind this.

169
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,960
He must have been framed by someone.

170
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,480
Just now,

171
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:36,900
the government office received a report

172
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:40,120
of a murder at the Qin residence in the north of the city.

173
00:11:40,640 --> 00:11:42,300
When the constables arrived,

174
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:44,920
they found the victim's body on the spot.

175
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:46,640
And at the scene,

176
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:50,840
only Jueming was sitting next to the victim,

177
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:53,200
holding a bloody dagger.

178
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:57,400
After verification, the dagger in Jueming's hand

179
00:11:57,600 --> 00:12:00,400
was indeed the murder weapon.

180
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:04,840
The shape of the blade perfectly matched the wound.

181
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:08,640
If you say he's not the suspect,

182
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:10,200
then who is?

183
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:12,680
Who reported the case?

184
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:15,100
If there was time to report it,

185
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:17,040
why didn't Jueming, as a suspect,

186
00:12:17,040 --> 00:12:18,320
flee immediately?

187
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:20,680
Why would he wait at the scene for the constables to arrive?

188
00:12:20,680 --> 00:12:23,600
I will naturally consider what you said.

189
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:28,240
But before Jueming's suspicion is cleared,

190
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:32,520
I cannot let him go for now.

191
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:35,200
Magistrate Zhao.

192
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,280
Miss Li.

193
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:47,800
I was transferred here as the county magistrate.

194
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:52,160
Upon arrival, I heard about your deeds.

195
00:12:52,560 --> 00:12:54,560
You have solved many strange cases.

196
00:12:54,800 --> 00:12:59,040
You even found the long-lost glazed orb of the Imperial Court.

197
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:02,680
But look closely at the people around you.

198
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:06,520
Su Yu'an was dismissed for perjury.

199
00:13:06,560 --> 00:13:08,760
Su Lang was imprisoned for murder.

200
00:13:08,800 --> 00:13:13,160
Only Jueming is left, and he is suspected of tonight's murder.

201
00:13:14,040 --> 00:13:17,800
Your colleagues are right beside you day and night.

202
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:20,680
Dare you guarantee

203
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:23,560
that you have seen right through them?

204
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:10,560
Jueming.

205
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:14,250
Why are you wearing these clothes?

206
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:15,820
What crime did you commit?

207
00:14:16,640 --> 00:14:17,640
That's not right.

208
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:19,800
My father came to me this morning

209
00:14:19,800 --> 00:14:22,480
and said you found the court's lost glazed orb together,

210
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:23,960
making a great contribution.

211
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:25,560
Squire Lu wrote to the court

212
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:28,260
to ask the Ministry of Justice to resentence me.

213
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:33,120
Squire Lu...

214
00:14:33,880 --> 00:14:35,040
He is dead.

215
00:14:35,520 --> 00:14:37,000
When did this happen?

216
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:38,160
Who killed him?

217
00:14:41,920 --> 00:14:43,180
They suspect it was me.

218
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:54,650
The victim and the evidence are both here.

219
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:57,640
You also have the victim's blood on you.

220
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,680
I think you are the murderer.

221
00:14:59,760 --> 00:15:00,760
Take him away.

222
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:03,720
Move.

223
00:15:09,440 --> 00:15:10,520
In that case,

224
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:12,880
did you see who knocked you out?

225
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:19,400
I was the only one at the crime scene.

226
00:15:20,880 --> 00:15:24,360
Looking at it this way, I am indeed the prime suspect.

227
00:15:24,640 --> 00:15:25,600
Oh, right.

228
00:15:25,760 --> 00:15:28,640
You hurried to the Qin Residence in the north of the city after receiving a note.

229
00:15:28,640 --> 00:15:29,440
Then we just need to find the note.

230
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:31,080
Since I fell into a trap,

231
00:15:31,760 --> 00:15:33,800
it was carefully planned by them.

232
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:37,080
They must have taken the note when I was knocked out.

233
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:38,400
I think

234
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:41,970
they've already taken the dart from my house.

235
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:45,680
What do we do now?

236
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:54,520
What I'm most worried about now

237
00:15:54,520 --> 00:15:56,800
is the two kids, Yichun and Nianxia.

238
00:15:57,800 --> 00:16:00,730
I hope when the killer went to my house to get the dart,

239
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,460
they didn't hurt them.

240
00:16:03,720 --> 00:16:04,560
Jueming.

241
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:08,240
I've already informed my father, Jueming.

242
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:09,840
Jueming.

243
00:16:09,880 --> 00:16:11,080
Father, Alang,

244
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:12,880
you've suffered.

245
00:16:13,360 --> 00:16:14,960
Are Yichun and Nianxia okay?

246
00:16:15,800 --> 00:16:16,760
Don't worry.

247
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:18,960
I've already brought them to the manor.

248
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:20,360
They won't be in danger.

249
00:16:21,400 --> 00:16:22,280
Thank you.

250
00:16:22,760 --> 00:16:23,960
Even though right now,

251
00:16:23,960 --> 00:16:26,720
I don't have evidence to prove your innocence,

252
00:16:26,920 --> 00:16:29,840
they can't prove you're the killer either.

253
00:16:31,080 --> 00:16:32,280
I will try my best.

254
00:16:33,280 --> 00:16:35,480
Think hard again. Think carefully.

255
00:16:35,520 --> 00:16:37,280
Did you miss any details?

256
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,920
Jinglan, Mr. Su.

257
00:16:40,640 --> 00:16:41,880
The dart outside my door

258
00:16:41,880 --> 00:16:44,600
and the files on my desk, are they still there?

259
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:49,360
The dart is gone.

260
00:16:49,480 --> 00:16:51,440
The files on the desk are gone too.

261
00:16:51,680 --> 00:16:53,280
The children were sleeping too soundly.

262
00:16:53,280 --> 00:16:55,600
They said they didn't hear a thing.

263
00:16:58,240 --> 00:16:59,440
His Lordship is here.

264
00:17:00,040 --> 00:17:00,600
Lord Li.

265
00:17:00,640 --> 00:17:01,760
You are all here.

266
00:17:01,800 --> 00:17:02,760
Open the door.

267
00:17:02,800 --> 00:17:03,560
Yes, sir.

268
00:17:13,480 --> 00:17:13,960
Su Lang.

269
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:14,530
Jueming,

270
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:16,760
don't panic.

271
00:17:16,920 --> 00:17:19,800
Even though I'm not familiar with the new magistrate,

272
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:21,880
he is still my subordinate.

273
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:25,000
If I order him to investigate this case thoroughly,

274
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:27,400
he won't dare to convict you without proof.

275
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:28,920
Yes, Jueming.

276
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:31,640
You must have dug into the higher-ups.

277
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:34,280
So they set a trap for you.

278
00:17:35,600 --> 00:17:38,440
This exactly proves my theory.

279
00:17:38,480 --> 00:17:40,540
I was looking in the right direction.

280
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:42,560
Mr. Su,

281
00:17:43,040 --> 00:17:43,880
there was a case back then

282
00:17:43,880 --> 00:17:47,340
called the Niutou Mountain child abduction and missing case.

283
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:49,960
Do you still remember the details?

284
00:17:50,960 --> 00:17:52,000
I remember.

285
00:17:53,320 --> 00:17:54,960
A woman came to report

286
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:58,040
that her child was abducted to Linhe Village

287
00:17:58,200 --> 00:18:00,060
and being raised by someone else.

288
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:01,970
We went to investigate,

289
00:18:02,080 --> 00:18:04,040
but when we found out, we realized

290
00:18:04,080 --> 00:18:05,760
it wasn't what she said.

291
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:09,160
Her child was indeed kidnapped,

292
00:18:09,800 --> 00:18:12,560
but by the time we found him,

293
00:18:12,840 --> 00:18:15,400
the child had suffocated in a sack.

294
00:18:15,560 --> 00:18:17,520
The woman couldn't take the shock

295
00:18:17,640 --> 00:18:19,280
and developed hysteria.

296
00:18:19,600 --> 00:18:22,880
Whenever she saw a child around her son's age,

297
00:18:23,080 --> 00:18:25,080
she would claim him as her own,

298
00:18:25,320 --> 00:18:26,720
causing a lot of trouble.

299
00:18:26,960 --> 00:18:27,960
But later,

300
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:31,160
we still caught the human trafficker

301
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:32,400
who abducted her son.

302
00:18:32,760 --> 00:18:33,760
All these years,

303
00:18:34,320 --> 00:18:35,960
every time I sold a child,

304
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:37,280
no matter what they were used for,

305
00:18:37,280 --> 00:18:38,520
I just took the money.

306
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:41,120
As for the child you mentioned,

307
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:43,380
running into him was just a coincidence.

308
00:18:44,800 --> 00:18:46,260
What kind of coincidence?

309
00:18:48,320 --> 00:18:51,880
That day, I was driving my carriage past Niutou Mountain.

310
00:18:57,840 --> 00:18:59,960
Uncle! Uncle!

311
00:19:05,280 --> 00:19:06,200
What's wrong?

312
00:19:07,200 --> 00:19:08,720
Over there! Over there!

313
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:21,720
We got a free one.

314
00:19:22,880 --> 00:19:24,680
There were four children in my carriage.

315
00:19:24,680 --> 00:19:25,960
Only he was suffocated to death.

316
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:28,560
I didn't mean to kill him.

317
00:19:36,360 --> 00:19:37,880
Come and identify.

318
00:19:38,080 --> 00:19:39,560
Where did the child get off,

319
00:19:39,560 --> 00:19:40,760
and where did you pick him up?

320
00:19:40,760 --> 00:19:41,960
Look closely.

321
00:19:45,480 --> 00:19:46,480
Here.

322
00:19:47,840 --> 00:19:49,200
Are you sure?

323
00:19:54,960 --> 00:19:55,880
Here.

324
00:20:07,520 --> 00:20:09,400
How did you die?

325
00:20:11,200 --> 00:20:12,960
I was murdered.

326
00:20:13,120 --> 00:20:14,760
Murdered?

327
00:20:16,280 --> 00:20:17,920
Did it hurt?

328
00:20:18,360 --> 00:20:20,120
It hurt a lot. Feel this.

329
00:20:20,160 --> 00:20:21,520
Stabbed so deep.

330
00:20:33,320 --> 00:20:34,920
How old are you?

331
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,040
Seven.

332
00:20:40,080 --> 00:20:42,240
Although you are highly suspicious,

333
00:20:42,320 --> 00:20:44,120
you are not the real killer.

334
00:20:44,240 --> 00:20:46,080
Because you are still young,

335
00:20:46,280 --> 00:20:48,480
and don't have enough strength

336
00:20:48,760 --> 00:20:50,400
to stab this deep.

337
00:20:50,680 --> 00:20:54,760
Besides, the murder weapon has a lingering floral scent,

338
00:20:54,800 --> 00:20:58,040
which means the murderer can only be...

339
00:21:01,280 --> 00:21:03,000
Can only be...

340
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:11,840
You don't clean up when you get up every day.

341
00:21:11,840 --> 00:21:13,160
The zither is gathering dust.

342
00:21:13,160 --> 00:21:15,280
You want to grow flowers but are too lazy to water them.

343
00:21:15,280 --> 00:21:18,760
Tell me, should I kill you?

344
00:21:19,600 --> 00:21:20,400
Mother.

345
00:21:20,520 --> 00:21:21,880
I know I was wrong.

346
00:21:23,440 --> 00:21:27,200
Grandpa, you can investigate cases even blindfolded!

347
00:21:27,320 --> 00:21:28,960
Of course I can.

348
00:21:29,560 --> 00:21:31,320
The details of the corpse

349
00:21:31,840 --> 00:21:36,000
and the smells on the body are all keys to solving the case.

350
00:21:37,160 --> 00:21:38,920
Well said, Mr. Qin.

351
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:42,000
Hearing this was truly enlightening

352
00:21:42,040 --> 00:21:43,880
and suddenly opened my mind.

353
00:21:44,840 --> 00:21:45,840
Isn't that right?

354
00:21:45,840 --> 00:21:47,360
Alright, stop flattering.

355
00:21:47,360 --> 00:21:48,280
The porridge is ready.

356
00:21:48,280 --> 00:21:49,440
Come over and help.

357
00:21:51,800 --> 00:21:52,960
What's good to eat?

358
00:21:57,800 --> 00:21:58,680
Here.

359
00:22:00,440 --> 00:22:01,840
It smells really good.

360
00:22:04,360 --> 00:22:07,040
Mrs. Qin, you put lotus seeds in it?

361
00:22:07,080 --> 00:22:09,720
Yes. Lotus seeds can nourish the heart and calm the mind,

362
00:22:09,720 --> 00:22:11,880
benefit the kidneys, and have a soft texture.

363
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:14,810
They also make the sweetness of the red beans richer.

364
00:22:16,760 --> 00:22:18,760
Mrs. Qin, after I finish eating,

365
00:22:18,840 --> 00:22:20,120
I want to take some home

366
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:22,800
for our little Su Lang to try, okay?

367
00:22:23,680 --> 00:22:24,480
How old is he?

368
00:22:24,520 --> 00:22:25,480
Come on.

369
00:22:25,680 --> 00:22:28,200
He is one year younger than Xiaonian.

370
00:22:29,840 --> 00:22:30,600
By the way,

371
00:22:31,760 --> 00:22:34,200
when you two go out these days,

372
00:22:34,360 --> 00:22:36,160
you must stick with your mother.

373
00:22:37,640 --> 00:22:40,800
The child kidnappers have been very rampant lately.

374
00:22:40,840 --> 00:22:42,480
You must be careful, hear me?

375
00:22:43,240 --> 00:22:45,160
Yes, let me tell you.

376
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:47,600
The missing children are about your age.

377
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:49,760
Just because they were playful and naughty,

378
00:22:49,760 --> 00:22:51,360
they came down the mountain by themselves,

379
00:22:51,360 --> 00:22:53,640
and met a bad guy driving a carriage,

380
00:22:53,720 --> 00:22:55,280
who took them all away.

381
00:22:56,520 --> 00:22:58,000
Second Uncle always lies.

382
00:22:58,040 --> 00:22:59,040
I don't believe it.

383
00:22:59,040 --> 00:23:00,000
Exactly.

384
00:23:00,040 --> 00:23:02,080
Me, lying?

385
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:04,560
Look here.

386
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:05,960
I even brought the map.

387
00:23:06,000 --> 00:23:07,640
This is the proof, see?

388
00:23:07,680 --> 00:23:08,800
They went missing right here.

389
00:23:08,800 --> 00:23:10,480
Why did you bring this out?

390
00:23:10,960 --> 00:23:15,040
Our Su Lang is even more naughty than them.

391
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:18,480
I have to show him the hard evidence to teach him a lesson.

392
00:23:18,640 --> 00:23:21,480
Bad guys want to kidnap you two. Are you afraid?

393
00:23:21,560 --> 00:23:23,240
I'm not afraid.

394
00:23:23,400 --> 00:23:25,760
Not afraid? Do you know if you get lost,

395
00:23:25,800 --> 00:23:27,640
how sad your parents would be?

396
00:23:33,600 --> 00:23:36,720
Has Vice Magistrate Cao been anywhere recently?

397
00:23:36,760 --> 00:23:38,640
For a round trip in a single day,

398
00:23:38,680 --> 00:23:41,560
Niutou Mountain is the only place nearby.

399
00:23:42,400 --> 00:23:46,200
Why would anyone go to Niutou Mountain alone?

400
00:23:49,040 --> 00:23:51,240
I have something to do. I'm heading out.

401
00:23:52,360 --> 00:23:53,880
Didn't you just get back?

402
00:23:53,920 --> 00:23:55,160
Come back soon.

403
00:23:56,160 --> 00:23:57,120
Constable Qin,

404
00:23:57,200 --> 00:23:58,800
today was supposed to be a day off.

405
00:23:58,800 --> 00:24:01,440
I already told my family I'd spend time with them.

406
00:24:01,440 --> 00:24:03,440
So I won't go with you.

407
00:24:08,160 --> 00:24:09,960
Come back early, Constable Qin.

408
00:24:11,840 --> 00:24:13,370
Sister-in-law, let's eat.

409
00:24:19,040 --> 00:24:20,480
Be careful.

410
00:24:21,440 --> 00:24:22,280
Mr. Su.

411
00:24:22,800 --> 00:24:24,720
How is the map marked?

412
00:24:27,480 --> 00:24:29,520
There are no special marks.

413
00:24:29,600 --> 00:24:30,960
It's just that this kid

414
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:33,760
came down from the west side of Niutou Mountain.

415
00:24:34,400 --> 00:24:36,260
The west side of Niutou Mountain.

416
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:39,600
Isn't that where the glazed orb and bones were found?

417
00:24:41,960 --> 00:24:43,600
You mean

418
00:24:43,720 --> 00:24:45,640
when this child came down the mountain,

419
00:24:45,640 --> 00:24:47,800
he witnessed a murder.

420
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:50,680
But before he could say it,

421
00:24:50,920 --> 00:24:52,680
he was... Cao Wen told me

422
00:24:53,360 --> 00:24:54,760
after Cao Shi died,

423
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:56,880
Constable Qin met Madam Cao.

424
00:24:58,040 --> 00:25:01,520
Constable Qin always felt there were suspicious points about Cao Shi's death.

425
00:25:01,520 --> 00:25:03,040
Madam Cao then told him

426
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:07,480
that Cao Shi did go to Niutou Mountain alone.

427
00:25:08,280 --> 00:25:09,160
Later,

428
00:25:09,440 --> 00:25:11,920
when Constable Qin looked at those map markings again,

429
00:25:11,920 --> 00:25:14,680
he thought of that child from back then

430
00:25:16,280 --> 00:25:18,210
who might have witnessed a murder.

431
00:25:19,160 --> 00:25:22,640
To verify his speculation without any evidence, Constable Qin

432
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:25,240
came to the west side of Niutou Mountain alone.

433
00:25:27,160 --> 00:25:29,840
He found a patch of freshly turned soil.

434
00:25:30,080 --> 00:25:32,000
He started digging from there

435
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:35,720
and eventually found Yexiao and the Liuli Pearl.

436
00:25:40,320 --> 00:25:43,640
Having learned the truth, he was immediately ambushed.

437
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:48,480
His bones were then buried together with the pearl.

438
00:25:49,440 --> 00:25:51,770
So this is how Constable Qin was murdered.

439
00:25:53,680 --> 00:25:55,960
I remember when I was little, you even used a map to teach me,

440
00:25:55,960 --> 00:25:57,560
telling me not to run around.

441
00:25:57,640 --> 00:25:59,720
That day was the Beginning of Spring.

442
00:26:01,440 --> 00:26:04,280
But after the fire at the Qin residence earlier,

443
00:26:04,400 --> 00:26:07,000
the charred corpse belonged to Constable Qin.

444
00:26:07,360 --> 00:26:08,200
No.

445
00:26:09,280 --> 00:26:10,520
It's the murderer's.

446
00:26:10,720 --> 00:26:13,840
How do you know it so well?

447
00:26:19,000 --> 00:26:21,200
Because I am Qin Rui's son,

448
00:26:23,880 --> 00:26:25,000
Qin Nian.

449
00:26:26,120 --> 00:26:27,040
This is terrifying.

450
00:26:27,040 --> 00:26:28,320
Yeah.

451
00:26:29,760 --> 00:26:31,040
During the festival,

452
00:26:31,720 --> 00:26:33,320
such a murder case happened.

453
00:26:33,480 --> 00:26:34,810
Where is Constable Qin?

454
00:26:35,240 --> 00:26:36,280
I don't know.

455
00:26:37,360 --> 00:26:39,200
I guess they'll be here soon.

456
00:26:40,120 --> 00:26:42,160
Stabbed dozens of times.

457
00:26:43,560 --> 00:26:45,680
Every strike hit a vital spot.

458
00:26:47,120 --> 00:26:49,680
The victim was a pharmacy lady.

459
00:26:50,360 --> 00:26:55,000
Why would the suspect be so ruthless?

460
00:27:06,640 --> 00:27:08,480
Who is she to you?

461
00:27:09,040 --> 00:27:10,560
My mother.

462
00:27:12,760 --> 00:27:14,840
Did you see the suspect?

463
00:27:19,280 --> 00:27:22,240
Is there anyone else at home?

464
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:43,660
You must be hungry. Eat something first.

465
00:27:53,600 --> 00:27:55,080
What's your name?

466
00:27:55,600 --> 00:27:56,680
Jueming.

467
00:27:56,840 --> 00:27:59,920
My mother was a medicine merchant. I was named after cassia seeds,

468
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:01,650
which means to improve vision.

469
00:28:02,360 --> 00:28:05,320
She gave you this name so you'd be clear-sighted

470
00:28:05,360 --> 00:28:06,680
and insightful.

471
00:28:08,680 --> 00:28:09,840
How old are you?

472
00:28:10,520 --> 00:28:11,480
Seven.

473
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:13,720
Same as me.

474
00:28:13,800 --> 00:28:15,040
What month were you born?

475
00:28:15,040 --> 00:28:15,920
May.

476
00:28:16,280 --> 00:28:17,600
I was born in November.

477
00:28:18,040 --> 00:28:19,800
Child, from now on,

478
00:28:19,840 --> 00:28:21,280
treat this as your home.

479
00:28:21,320 --> 00:28:24,000
Wan'er is 10. She'll be your older sister.

480
00:28:24,040 --> 00:28:25,960
Niannian is 7. He'll be your younger brother.

481
00:28:25,960 --> 00:28:26,840
Okay?

482
00:28:33,280 --> 00:28:34,960
My mother used to travel a lot.

483
00:28:35,000 --> 00:28:37,480
She always forbade me from leaving the house.

484
00:28:37,480 --> 00:28:40,680
Whenever I missed her, I would look at this portrait.

485
00:28:41,240 --> 00:28:44,040
Now, I will never see her again.

486
00:28:45,120 --> 00:28:46,760
It's okay. From now on,

487
00:28:46,920 --> 00:28:48,480
this is your home.

488
00:28:48,560 --> 00:28:51,160
Tell us whenever you are unhappy.

489
00:28:51,560 --> 00:28:54,280
We will carefully glue your mother's portrait back together.

490
00:28:54,280 --> 00:28:56,480
You can look at it whenever you miss her.

491
00:28:57,520 --> 00:28:58,920
Give the painting to me.

492
00:29:01,600 --> 00:29:03,120
Mother, I'm going out for a bit.

493
00:29:03,120 --> 00:29:04,320
I'll be right back.

494
00:29:04,440 --> 00:29:05,200
Okay.

495
00:29:06,280 --> 00:29:07,200
Slow down.

496
00:29:18,560 --> 00:29:19,600
It's mended.

497
00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:21,720
This is the best I can do.

498
00:29:22,080 --> 00:29:23,840
That will be three coins.

499
00:29:24,320 --> 00:29:25,360
Thank you.

500
00:29:29,080 --> 00:29:30,240
Just like that.

501
00:29:33,320 --> 00:29:35,200
That day, after the painting was mended,

502
00:29:35,200 --> 00:29:36,560
I ran all the way back.

503
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:40,240
But when I returned home,

504
00:29:41,040 --> 00:29:44,800
I saw a scene I will never forget.

505
00:30:07,560 --> 00:30:09,720
Your Honor, the five members of the Qin family,

506
00:30:09,720 --> 00:30:11,880
two adults and two children, are all accounted for.

507
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:12,840
Once this fire burns,

508
00:30:12,840 --> 00:30:15,100
no one will dare to investigate further.

509
00:30:22,320 --> 00:30:26,280
With you, the numbers add up.

510
00:30:28,480 --> 00:30:30,000
No one knew

511
00:30:30,720 --> 00:30:32,520
that the child who died back then

512
00:30:32,560 --> 00:30:33,880
wasn't Qin Nian.

513
00:30:39,040 --> 00:30:39,960
After that,

514
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:43,960
I took on Jueming's identity

515
00:30:44,880 --> 00:30:46,120
and survived.

